des: The number one question I get asked in social settings is whats going on in the Real Estate market?? As a Realtor I love to educate people on all the happenings in todays market in Snohomish County and beyond. We'll go over weekly anything from sales prices, offer frenzy, interest rates and more! All info coming from your burning real estate questions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
